，是屬於排便排汗的時段，而不是補充營養的時段 。腸胃等消化器官在排泄時段還沒睡醒，而掌握人體活動的「酵素」也還在休眠， 這個時候吃早餐，維持人體健康的「酵素」便無法充分運作，很容易就會造成消化不良 。<br />\n不吃早餐更健康<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/0317vkt0017-1024_11911086255a5dd66150cb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F0317vkt0017-1024_11911086255a5dd66150cb7.jpg&h=9d0cc459&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"901768c0b5b9766d783dcc4576736d64200f4778","tid":1052550,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"學左動漫角色 我朝早一包一野飲 十零蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb9c30c991befd0112368d9fa6cdc92a19a9fda","tid":1052550,"uid":32205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"901768c0b5b9766d783dcc4576736d64200f4778","tid":1052550,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"學左動漫角色 我朝早一包一野飲 十零蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"lunch 夜晚唔食？"},{"pid":"15dbc6d6d3874c9421dc80e27912ba7f1556c061","tid":1052550,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"樓主在不在。關於買磚想請教"},{"pid":"8f0b2fa36e7e4bf769526d7616c43396d2736503","tid":1052550,"uid":32205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15dbc6d6d3874c9421dc80e27912ba7f1556c061","tid":1052550,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"樓主在不在。關於買磚想請教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"買咩磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪認錯人"},{"pid":"59f06f68099241269607901aa9ae707520c00aeb","tid":1052550,"uid":25653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f0b2fa36e7e4bf769526d7616c43396d2736503","tid":1052550,"uid":32205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15dbc6d6d3874c9421dc80e27912ba7f1556c061","